            <title>[LANG-911] UTF8 4byte (un)escapeJava not work correctly</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LANG-911</link>
                <project id="12310481" key="LANG">Commons Lang</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;String bellsTest = &quot;\ud83d\udc80\ud83d\udd14&quot;;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;String value = StringEscapeUtils.escapeJava(bellsTest);&lt;br/&gt;
String valueTest = StringEscapeUtils.unescapeJava(value);&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;System.out.println(bellsTest);&lt;br/&gt;
System.out.println(value);&lt;br/&gt;
System.out.println(valueTest);&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Error:&lt;br/&gt;
!!!  bellsTest (befor) != valueTest (after escapeJava&amp;amp;unescapeJava)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
